OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfficers told not to wear  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpolice uniforms at Pride   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Police officers who wish to attend this
OL,6, year's Pride march in Belfast will not 
OL,7, be allowed to do so in uniform.        
OL,9,FAssistant Chief Constable Bobby        
OL,10,FSingleton said: "I know this decision  
OL,11,Fwill come as a disappointment to some."
OL,13,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland     
OL,14,F(PSNI) officers first paraded in       
OL,15,Funiform at the event in 2017.          
OL,17,FBut police have faced criticism as some
OL,18,Fhave seen their attendance as an       
OL,19,Fofficial endorsement of gay rights     
OL,20,Fcampaign issues.                       
